0.002  2012-12-12

 - (Addition) Allow Carpish shortcuts for failure callbacks.
 - (Bugfix) Ensure that $! is set even if failure callback dies.
 - (Documentation) Document test suite.
 - (Packaging) Skip the bulk of the test suite on MSWin32.

